cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper involves the use of deep neural networks for image analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of multiple modalities and scales in the analysis suggests a potential fit for the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
